ation-the-path-to-quantum-advantage</link><description>量子计算机可以帮助组织做出更好的决策吗？量子优化工作组的一项新研究描绘了前进的方向。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/multi-objective-optimization-the-path-to-quantum-advantage.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 10:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/multi-objective-optimization-the-path-to-quantum-advantage</guid></item><item><title>少数沙漠蓝藻和藻类负责大量二氧化碳固定</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-minority-of-desert-cyanobacteria-and-algae-is-responsible-for-the-bulk-of-co2-fixation</link><description>蓝藻和藻类是沙漠中主要的光合生物，因为它们比其他植物更能适应干燥、高太阳辐射和极端温度波动。在有利的条件下，沙漠蓝藻和藻类明显进行光合作用。然而，我们对每个群体是否会调节这种代谢过程以应对先前的恶劣条件的理解仍然有限。为了找出干旱对沙漠蓝藻和藻类光合活性的影响，我们比较了它们的细胞生物体积特定二氧化碳（CO &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-minority-of-desert-cyanobacteria-and-algae-is-responsible-for-the-bulk-of-co2-fixation2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 10:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-minority-of-desert-cyanobacteria-and-algae-is-responsible-for-the-bulk-of-co2-fixation</guid></item><item><title>草原芽和芽的人口统计取决于氮添加的数量和频率</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/grassland-bud-and-shoot-demography-depend-on-both-amount-and-frequency-of-nitrogen-addition</link><description>🌱草原芽和芽对氮添加的反应取决于添加的频率。频繁、小剂量的用药比大剂量、不频繁的用药对新生长的损害更小。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/grassland-bud-and-shoot-demography-depend-on-both-amount-and-frequency-of-nitrogen-addition2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 10:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/grassland-bud-and-shoot-demography-depend-on-both-amount-and-frequency-of-nitrogen-addition</guid></item></channel></rss>